{"tid":1240590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"777: 建制派要預先提供民意的推敲","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:41:27.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2dccd56424742bf395961e2329e71383050fac3","tid":1240590,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463630-20190618.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463630-20190618.htm&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=a1ac14a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463630-20190618.htm&h=ccc875e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463630-20190618.htm</a><br />\n有反對修訂《逃犯條例》的示威者早前墮樓身亡，行政長官林鄭月娥在記者會被問到，會否為犠牲了示威者而下台負責，她表示，呼籲每個市民用和平及理性的方法，就著社會議題表達意見；如果用某一種行為令自己受到傷害，都是不能預見。她為示威者因為表達意見傷害自己而感到非常難過。<br />\n<br />\n至於她與建制派的關係，林鄭月娥對於建制派承受批評感到歉意，包括由始至終支持她的建制派議員。她希望，日後的行政立法關係建基於「對事不對人」，能與各黨派議員合作，但由於她與建制派的互動機會較多，往後歡迎在施政方面預先提供民意的推敲。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，目前已沒有法律基礎，在台灣殺人案嫌疑犯於今年10月刑滿出獄前處理這宗案件，她感到令人遺憾。"},{"pid":"55a8b1277132ddae59cd161906ebea01cf62557f","tid":1240590,"uid":123115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"仆街 啱啱Bloomberg 話佢mention 佢會withdraw the very first time <br />\n我屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3cvBNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3cvBNd.png&h=11d842d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B210Y0A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB210Y0A.png&h=c63049aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc7bbf6845ce7990a8cf4f60112726095005d54","tid":1240590,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}